snippet.title: Ages of Cataria - A village story generator game
snippet.description:
Live on Kickstarter https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1357767389/colonies-of-cataria-online-colony-sim-game

Ages of Cataria is a village story generator where you get to learn about the citizens that make up your town. Experience the real-time growth of your village and watch your villagers develop their own stories over time.

Live on Kickstarter https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1357767389/colonies-of-cataria-online-colony-sim-game

Discord: https://discord.gg/22TmNMvWZX
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/agesofcataria
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AgesofCataria
Instagram:https://www.instagram.com/agesofcataria/
